Story.create(title: 'Boulette has the high ground', pet: 'Boulette', content: 'Unbeknownst to us, Boulette can climb the tallest hidey of the cage. One evening, we found her resting on top of it, looking down at her kingdom, just chilling. Luckily, she did not hurt herself.', tldr:'Boulette climbed the tallest hidey just to chill there')
Story.create(title: 'Burrito takes a leap of faith', pet: 'Burrito', content: 'One afternoon, we were grooming Burrito. She was calm as usual, as she is a scaredy cat. Maybe she got spooked by a bird outside, maybe it was a popcorn gone wrong. Anyways, she jumped off the couch, and right into the window. A few drops of disinfectant after, she was good as new, although quite scared.', tldr:'Burrito jumped into a window for no reason.')
Story.create(title: 'Nuggy is chonky', pet: 'Nugget', content: 'Nugget is the head of the herd. As such, she starts eating first, finishes last and eats most of the pellets. Weirdly enough, she is the one that puts on the most weight. One day, we realized she was becoming pear-shaped. Now Nugget is hand-fed a few pellets a day only. ...When we have time.', tldr:'Nugget is getting chubby because she hogs all the food')
